THE MISSION OF 1SS 1SS is a research laboratory set up by the Singapore government to undertake world class research in information technology, with a mission to effect technology transfer in partnership with international and Singapore-based corporations. 1SS research is directed to producing inventions and prototypes Ieadmg to the development of a next generation of information systems. With a research staff of around 100 and rising, 1SS is currently concentrating on 3 technology areas multimedia systems, artilcial intelligence, and multilingual applications.